Detailed Description

cvmx_sli_pkt_int

This register combines the SLI_PKT_CNT_INT, SLI_PKT_TIME_INT or SLI_PKT_IN_INT interrupt registers. When read by a function, this register informs which rings owned by the function (0 to N, N as large as 63) have an interrupt pending.
